StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: UPDATEOFFICE
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.UPDATEOFFICE(pOldNum IN VARCHAR2, pBuildingCode IN VARCHAR2, &lt;br/&gt; pNewNum IN VARCHAR2, pOfficePhone IN NUMBER) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; UPDATE Office_table office&lt;br/&gt; SET office.buildingCode = pBuildingCode,&lt;br/&gt; office.officeNumber = pNewNum,&lt;br/&gt; office.officePhone = pOfficePhone&lt;br/&gt; WHERE office.officeNumber = pOldNum;&lt;br/&gt;END updateOffice;
